The paper proposes an algorithm for solving the longest path problem in undirected weighted graphs, which involves graph partitioning and dynamic programming. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). However, since the paper focuses on algorithm design and optimization, it is most likely to belong to cs.DM or cs.DS.
